'''八角金盤'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Fatsia japonica''）是[[八角金盤屬|八角金盤屬]]下的一個種，是一種原産於[[日本|日本]]南部的常綠灌木。高度可達{{convert|3|-|6|m}}。

八角金盤是常見的觀賞植物，在冬天溫度不低於零下十五攝氏度的地區都可以生存。已被證實可去除室內[[甲醛|甲醛]]。<ref name="JASHS2008">{{Cite journal|title=Efficiency of Volatile Formaldehyde Removal by Indoor Plants: Contribution of Aerial Plant Parts versus the Root Zone|url=https://journals.ashs.org/jashs/view/journals/jashs/133/4/article-p521.xml|last=Kim|first=Kwang Jin|last2=Kil|first2=Mi Jung|date=2008-07-01|journal=Journal of the American Society for Horticultural Science|issue=4|doi=10.21273/JASHS.133.4.521|volume=133|pages=521–526|language=en-US|issn=2327-9788|last3=Song|first3=Jeong Seob|last4=Yoo|first4=Eun Ha|last5=Son|first5=Ki-Cheol|last6=Kays|first6=Stanley J.|access-date=2021-09-14|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215123114/https://journals.ashs.org/jashs/view/journals/jashs/133/4/article-p521.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

八角金盤和其培育種''F. japonica'' 'Variegata'已獲得[[皇家園藝學會|皇家園藝學會]]優秀園藝獎（Award of Garden Merit）。<ref>{{cite web|title=RHS Plant Selector - ''Fatsia japonica''|url=http://apps.rhs.org.uk/plantselector/plant?plantid=788|accessdate=19 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414120606/http://apps.rhs.org.uk/plantselector/plant?plantid=788|archive-date=2014-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=RHS Plant Selector - ''Fatsia japonica'' 'Variegata'|url=http://apps.rhs.org.uk/plantselector/plant?plantid=2932|accessdate=19 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414113408/http://apps.rhs.org.uk/plantselector/plant?plantid=2932|archive-date=2014-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

